  "rationale": "<p class=\"tcp-1f880b6e-38f9-491c-967b-0a0203d4c894\">Choice A is correct. By distributing the minus sign through the expression <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"two thirds x minus 5\"></span>, the given expression can be rewritten as&nbsp;<span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, one half x plus 3, close parenthesis, minus two thirds x, plus 5\"></span>, which is equivalent to <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one half x, minus two thirds x, plus 3, plus 5\"></span>. Combining like terms gives <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, one half minus two thirds, close parenthesis, times x, plus, open parenthesis, 3 plus 5, close parenthesis\"></span>, or <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"negative one sixth x plus 8\"></span>.<p>Choice B is incorrect and may be the result of failing to distribute the minus sign appropriately through the second term and simplifying the expression <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one half x, plus 3, minus two thirds x, minus 5\"></span>. Choice C is incorrect and may be the result of multiplying the expressions&nbsp;<span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one half x plus 3 \"></span> and <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"negative two thirds x plus 5\"></span>. Choice D is incorrect and may be the result of multiplying the expressions <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one half x plus 3 \"></span> and <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"negative two thirds x minus 5\"></span>.</p></p>\n",
